edia.org/resource/Berlin_International_Film_Festival\">Berlin International Film Festival</a> for <i><a href=\"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caesar_Must_Die\">Caesar Must Die</a></i>.", "2012: <a href=\"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_di_Donatello_for_Best_Film\">David di Donatello for Best Film</a> and <a href=\"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_di_Donatello_for_Best_Director\">David di Donatello for Best Director</a> for <a href=\"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caesar_Must_Die\">Caesar Must Die</a>."]], "subsections": []}]}]}}